         <abstract>
            <p>The acts of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2536BatraGe">Batergelā Māryām</persName> are only preserved as three miracles within the 
            <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2384Taamme"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2384Taamme</span></ref>: <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5255MiracleBatergela1"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT5255MiracleBatergela1</span></ref>,<ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5256MiracleBatergela2"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT5256MiracleBatergela2</span></ref> 
