         <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="mir1" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5255MiracleBatergela1"><label>Miracle 1</label>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <note>This incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML3872"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: EMML3872</span></ref>.</note>
               <ab>
                  ዘገብረት፡ ተአምረ፡ ወመንክረ፡ ለአሐቲ፡ ብእሲተ፡ መስፍን፡ በኃይለ፡ ወልዳ፡ ፍቁር። ጸሎታ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS6437Macomber"/>
                  ወሀሎ፡ አሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ መስፍን፡ በአሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ዐባይ፡ እምአህጉረ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወቦቱ፡ ብእሲተ፡ እምዘመደ፡ ኄራን፡ ወስፉቀ፡ ፍቅረ፡ ያፈቅራ።
               </ab>
            </div></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="mir2" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5256MiracleBatergela2"><label>Miracle 2</label>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <note>This incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML3872"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: EMML3872</span></ref>.</note>
               <ab>
                  ዘገብረት፡ ተአምረ፡ ወመንክረ፡ ለዝኩ፡ ወልድ፡ በተርጌላ፡ ማርያም። ጸሎታ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS6437Macomber"/>
                  ወኮነ፡ ሶበ፡ ልህቀ፡ ዝኩ፡ ሕፃን፡ በቴርጌላ፡ ማርያም፡ ይጸመድ፡ ወትረ፡ በዴዴ፡ መስፍን።
               </ab>
            </div></div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="mir3" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5257MiracleBatergela3"><label>Miracle 3</label>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <note>This incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML3872"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: EMML3872</span></ref>.</note>
               <ab>
                  ዘገብረት፡ ሎቱ፡ ተአምረ፡ ወመንክረ፡ ለገብረ፡ ዚአሃ፡ በቴርጌላ፡ ማርያም። ጸሎታ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS6437Macomber"/>
                  ወኮነ፡ ሶበ፡ በዝኃ፡ ሕማመ፡ ብድብድ፡ ላዕለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ምድር፡ በዴዴ፡ መስፍን፡ አዘዞሙ፡ መስፍን፡
                  ለወልዱ፡ ወለአዋልዲሁ፡ ወለኵሉ፡ ዕድ፡ ወአንስት፡ አዘዞሙ፡ ይትማህለሉ፡ ኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ልዑል፡ ወኀበ፡ እግዝእትነ።
               </ab>
            </div></div>
